section_title: Clarification of the Text in Section G (Article 3.7ter) of the Doha Amendment to the Kyoto Protocol
sentences: Co-Chair Anke Herold presented draft conclusions to continue consideration of this matter at SBSTA 43, taking into account the annexed options for draft decision elements.

Following discussions on the annex, the contact group put brackets around section II on options related to "average annual emissions" of the draft decision and agreed to forward the draft conclusions for SBSTA§s consideration.
